video.title: Rare but Super Useful HTML tags that will turn you into a web ninja
video.description:
In this video we are covering some of the useful and productive , but rare html5 tags that will help you to become better web developer. These tags will save a lot of your time and make you more productive. 
These HTML tags have nice support in most modern browsers and we can use them instead of implementing 100s of custom features.

Timeline:
--------------------------------------
00:00 Details+Summary Tags
00:51 Awesome Input Types
02:41 Meter Tag
03:03 Progress Tag
03:55 Datalist tag
05:32 Optgroup tag
06:08 (BONUS) js .closest() function

INPUT TYPES COVERED
--------------------------------------
Input Type Color
Input Type range
Input Type Date
Input Type DateTime-Local
Input Type Time
Input Type Week
